quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  39,57,"maa ki wi'a: \"Si Alah fewnuno lam, mi wonanyno jeyaa…óo e gom…óu…ìe …ìen"
  39,58,"Maa ki wi'a, tuma ki yi'ata lepte …óen: \"Si feere ruttagol no woodannoo lam, mi jeyee e mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  39,59,"Gasataa ! Tawde Aayeeje Am …óen aruno e maa…óa, fennu…óaa …óe, mawnintini…óaa, laati…óaa jeyaa…óo e yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  39,60,"√ëalnde Darngal, a yi'oya fennonoo…ìe e hoore Allah …ìen, hino …ìawli geece. Wonaa ka Jahannama woni jaa∆¥orde mawnintinii…ìe …ìen"
  39,61,"Allah na da…óndira gom…óu…ìe …ìen, sabu maloore ma…ì…ìe nden. Bone memataa …ìen, wanaa kam…ìe woni sunoytoo…ìe"
  39,62,"Ko Allah woni Tagu…óo kala huunde, ko Kanko kadi woni Fawtii…óo kala huunde"
  39,63,"Ko Kanko sottir…óe kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin woodani. Yeddu…ìe Aayeeje Allah …ìen non, ko …ìen woni hayru…ìe(pertu…ìe) …ìen"
  39,64,"Maaku: \"E ko woori Allah, yamirton mi, yo mi rewu, onon …ìee majju…ìe"
  39,65,"Gom…óii wahayinaama e maa…óa, e …ìen adinoo…ìe ma: \"Si a sirkii, pellet, golle maa …óen bonay jeye…óaa e hayru…ìe …ìen"
  39,66,"Alah rew Allah, jeye…óaa e yettoo…ìe (Mo) …ìen"
  39,67,"∆Åe mawniniraali Allah, no O foti maninireede, hara le, leydi ndin fow, ko tamannde Makko, √ëalnde Darngal, kammuuli …óin kadi taggiree √±aamo Makko. Senayee woodanii Mo ! O toowii e kon ko …ìe sirkanta Mo"
